wonderful stay.", "time": 1752045446, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Chris Sedlacek", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103376037139991336636/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLqIfx9Mi5pY16GfrcoITPXNk2qgpmqQGQesMULkSEWZ-VsP_V0A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating": 4, "relative_time_description": "3 months ago", "text": "I really enjoyed my stay at Hotel Bayard. The location is fantastic, the staff were attentive, and the facility is beautiful, with spacious accommodations and carefully curated vintage decor throughout. By far, one of the most uniquely decorated and furnished hotels I have stayed. Breakfast was wonderful as well. My only complaint is on the cleanliness of the room. It was apparent that the floors had not been cleaned in some time; a simple vacuum and mop would have done the trick. Otherwise, a pleasant stay and would recommend.", "time": 1749572172, "translated": false}], "secondary_opening_hours": [{"open_now": false, "periods": [{"close": {"date": "2025-10-05", "day": 0, "time": "1100"}, "open": {"date": "2025-10-05", "day": 0, "time": "0700"}}, {"close": {"date": "2025-10-06", "day": 1, "time": "1100"}, "open": {"date": "2025-10-06", "day": 1, "time": "0700"}}, {"close": {"date": "2025-10-07", "day": 2, "time": "1100"}, "open": {"date": "2025-10-07", "day": 2, "time": "0700"}}, {"close": {"date": "2025-10-08", "day": 3, "time": "1100"}, "open": {"date": "2025-10-08", "day": 3, "time": "0700"}}, {"close": {"date": "2025-10-09", "day": 4, "time": "1100"}, "open": {"date": "2025-10-09", "day": 4, "time": "0700"}}, {"close": {"date": "2025-10-10", "day": 5, "time": "1100"}, "open": {"date": "2025-10-10", "day": 5, "time": "0700"}}, {"close": {"date": "2025-10-04", "day": 6, "time": "1100"}, "open": {"date": "2025-10-04", "day": 6, "time": "0700"}}], "type": "BREAKFAST", "weekday_text": ["Monday: 7:00\u2009\u2013\u200911:00\u202fAM", "Tuesda